    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "> Love that! Is it possible to offer two builds?\n\nYes feasible, but how would we guide users towards them? As a user of instantsearch.js I am not aware of either React or preact so not sure how I could make a choice.\n\nBut it's a good idea to be able start testing this build yes. We could also just push it and see what happens. Our heavy demo is working with it so if we have glitches they should not happen on that many websites.\n",
