  {
    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Since we were exposing that we accepted React components as templates and it was accessible in the production build, I had to rollback the default build and create a specific preact build. This should not be an issue in ISV2 where we will completely hide the fact that we use react/preact for non react users.\n",
